  "description": "<p>🚚 <strong>Hiring: Replenish Driver (Class 3)</strong></p><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> West<br />🗓 <strong>Working Days:</strong> 5 days per week<br />🚐 <strong>Vehicle:</strong> Company van provided</p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><p>Replenish stocks at retail outlets/malls<br />Manage and top up stock levels on shelves<br />Ensure proper display and stock accuracy<br />Simple stock handling and reporting</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>Valid Class 3 driving licence<br />Responsible and reliable<br />Able to manage physical work</p><p>🎁 <strong>Staff Benefits:</strong> Provided<br /><br />Interested parties:</p><p>Click ''<strong>APPLY</strong>'' or<br />Send your resume to <em><strong>admin@psmanpower.com </strong></em>with the subject line: “<strong>JRDR3135</strong><em><strong> Application</strong></em>”<br /><br />Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br />By applying for this role, you consent to PS Manpower Pte Ltd PDPA<br />Data collected is strictly used for recruitment purposes only.</p>",
